="preserve">"I Don't Want to Be'" is the debut single by Gavin DeGraw on his first album "Chariot". The single was released in 2004. The song is in the Alternative rock genre.
Chart Rankings.
U.S. "Billboard" Hot 100 gave the single "I Don't Wanna Be" a ranking of #10, U.K. Singles Chart gave the single a ranking of #32, and Dutch Singles Chart ranked it at #9.
